cdata.name: Giant
cdata.desc:
Giant (GIC) is a PoW/PoS Masternode cryptocurrency based on the Quark algorithm. It is a cryptocurrency designed to work with the Giant exchange,a decentralized exchange built on top of blockchain technology, which provides the exchange rate ofseveral cryptocurrencies, such as BTC, ETH, XRP, LTC.

GICfeatures a second layer network of masternodes that process private and near-instant transactions.
